#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Application Info Endpoint"
msgstr "应用程序信息端点"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus-info` extension exposes an HTTP endpoint at `/q/info` that returns information about the application: build metadata, git commit, Java version, and operating system."
msgstr "`quarkus-info` 扩展在 `/q/info` 处提供了一个 HTTP 端点，该端点会返回有关应用程序的信息：构建元数据、Git 提交、Java 版本以及操作系统。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Adding the extension"
msgstr "添加扩展程序"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Add the `quarkus-info` extension to your project:"
msgstr "将 `quarkus-info` 扩展添加到您的项目中："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This will add the following to your build file:"
msgstr "这将在您的构建文件中添加以下内容："

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "pom.xml"
msgstr "pom.xml"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "build.gradle"
msgstr "build.gradle"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Once added, start your application and access the info endpoint:"
msgstr "添加完成后，启动您的应用程序并访问该信息端点："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Response structure"
msgstr "响应结构"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The endpoint returns a JSON object with up to four sections:"
msgstr "该端点返回一个 JSON 对象，其中最多包含四个部分："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Each section can be individually enabled or disabled via configuration."
msgstr "每个部分均可通过配置单独启用或禁用。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Git information is only available if the project is in a Git repository. If no `.git` directory is found, the `git` section is omitted."
msgstr "只有当项目位于 Git 仓库中时，才会显示 Git 信息。如果未找到 `.git` 目录，则省略 `Git` 部分。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Git information modes"
msgstr "Git 信息模式"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus.info.git.mode` property controls how much git information is included."
msgstr "`quarkus.info.git.mode` 属性用于控制包含多少 Git 信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`standard` (default)"
msgstr "`标准` （默认）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Branch name, abbreviated commit ID, and commit time."
msgstr "分支名称、提交 ID 缩写和提交时间。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`full`"
msgstr "`完整`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Adds remote URL, tags, full commit ID, commit message, author and committer details."
msgstr "添加远程 URL、标签、完整提交 ID、提交信息、作者以及提交者详细信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With `full` mode, the `git` section expands to:"
msgstr "在 `完整` 模式下， `git` 部分展开为："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Adding custom build properties"
msgstr "添加自定义构建属性"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can add custom key-value pairs to the `build` section:"
msgstr "您可以在 `“build”` 部分添加自定义键值对："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "These will appear alongside the standard build properties:"
msgstr "这些将与标准构建属性并列显示："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Custom info contributors"
msgstr "自定义信息贡献者"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can contribute your own sections to the info endpoint by implementing the `InfoContributor` interface and making it a CDI bean:"
msgstr "您可以通过实现 `InfoContributor` 接口并将其作为 CDI Bean，向 info 端点贡献自己的章节："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This adds a `custom` section to the info endpoint response:"
msgstr "这会在 info 端点的响应中添加一个 `自定义` 部分："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `name()` method determines the key in the JSON output.\n"
"The `data()` method is called once at startup, use it for values that don't change at runtime."
msgstr "`name()` 方法用于确定 JSON 输出中的键。 `data()` 方法在启动时调用一次，请将其用于运行时不会发生变化的值。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Programmatic access"
msgstr "程序化访问"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The extension also exposes injectable beans that you can use directly in your code:"
msgstr "该扩展还提供了可注入的 Bean，您可以在代码中直接使用它们："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The available beans are:"
msgstr "可选的豆类有："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`GitInfo`: `branch()`, `latestCommitId()`, `commitTime()`"
msgstr "`GitInfo` ： `branch()` 、 `latestCommitId()` 、 `commitTime()`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`BuildInfo`: `group()`, `artifact()`, `version()`, `time()`, `quarkusVersion()`"
msgstr "`BuildInfo` ： `group()` 、 `artifact()` 、 `version()` 、 `time()` 、 `quarkusVersion()`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`JavaInfo`: `version()`, `vendor()`, `vendorVersion()`"
msgstr "`JavaInfo` ： `version()` 、 `vendor()` 、 `vendorVersion()`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`OsInfo`: `name()`, `version()`, `architecture()`"
msgstr "`OsInfo` ： `name()` 、 `version()` 、 `architecture()`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "These beans are only available if the corresponding section is enabled in configuration."
msgstr "只有在配置中启用了相应的部分，才能使用这些豆类。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Management interface"
msgstr "管理界面"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you use the xref:management-interface-reference.adoc[management interface], the info endpoint is automatically exposed on the management port instead of the main HTTP port:"
msgstr "如果您 xref:management-interface-reference.adoc[使用管理界面，] 则 info 端点会自动在管理端口上暴露，而不是在主 HTTP 端口上："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/info.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The info endpoint will then be available at `http://0.0.0.0:9000/q/info` instead of `http://localhost:8080/q/info`."
msgstr "届时，info 端点的访问地址将变为 `http://0.0.0.0:9000/q/info` ，而非 `http://localhost:8080/q/info` 。"

